div.div:
When a replica becomes a new proposer. It sends its latest lid to all other ready replicas to check if it has any missing log record due to the preivous primary failure. Other acceptor replica sends back the list of missing logs if the new proposer is lagged and the lastLid that it has.
If there is also a new replica, then the new proposer should complete new replica addition AFTER proposer confirmation.
